<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA34">
<l>āmā ṟaṟiyāvē valviṉaika ḷantarattē</l>
<l>nāmāḷeṉ ṟēttār nakarmūṉṟum - vēmā</l>
<l>ṟorukaṇaiyāṟ ceṟṟāṉai yuḷḷattā luḷḷi</l>
<l>yarukaṇaiyā tārai yaṭum</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The harsh deeds that do not know the way it is, they will kill</l>
<l>those who do not seek the proximity, thinking with [their] minds</l>
<l>of him who subdued with one arrow in the way that all the three cities in space burned,</l>
<l>of those who did not praise “we are [your] servants”.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
